Questions.Name: Pit Questions
Questions.Description: Questions to ask teams in the Pit

Pit Questions.Question: What chassis type is your robot?
How tall is your chassis?
What is your primary objective?
What is your secondary objective?
Where can your robot shoot fuel?
Can your robot climb the rope?
Does your robot stay up when it goes up?
Do you use your own rope?
Do you have to be right on top of the rope to climb?
Does your robot place gears?
How do you pick up fuel? (floor)
How do you pick up fuel? (feeder station)
How do you pick up fuel? (hopper)
Where can you put your human players? (airship)
Where can you put your human players? (feeder station)
Where can you put your human players? (overflow)
Where can you put your human players? (runner)
Do you have autonomous?
Where do you score from in autonomous? (move forward)
Where do you score from in autonomous? (place gear)
Where do you score from in autonomous? (shoot into boiler)
Where can you pick up gears?
Where can you pick up fuel?
How is your team willing to play?
What are your strengths?
What are your weaknesses?
On a scale of 1 to 10 what is your robot's maneuverability?
How many feet per second can your robot travel?
How many years has your driver been driving?
How many years has your manipulator been manipulating your robot?
How quickly can you do a full cycle?
Fuel firing? (high)
Fuel firing? (low)
Fuel firing? (single)
Fuel firing? (multi)
What drivetrain do you have?
What position does your team start at? (closest stands)
What position does your team start at? (middle)
What position does your team start at? (closest pit)
How experienced is your Drive Team? (How many years of Drive team do they have)?
What type of shooter does your robot have?

Questions.Name: Match Questions
Questions.Description: Questions you answer in the stand during the match

Autonomous Questions.Question: Did the robot cross the line?
Did the robot score high boiler?
Did the robot score low boiler?
Did the robot activate the hopper?
What starting pieces did they start out with?
Which position did they start off in?
How many penalties did they accumulate?

Tele-op Questions.Question: How many gears did they score?
Did they attempt to score high boiler?
Tele-op Questions.Comment: If they attempt to score, show the next question

Tele-op Questions.Question: How many trips did they take to score in the high boiler?
Did they attempt to score the low boiler?
Tele-op Questions.Comment: If they do attempt to score low boiler, show the next question

Tele-op Questions.Question: How many trips did they take to score in the low boiler?
Did they receive a technical foul?
Tele-op Questions.Comment: We're not exactly sure if there is such thing

Tele-op Questions.Question: Did they receive a Yellow Card?
Did they receive a Red Card?
Did they play defensively or offensively?

End-Game Questions.Question: How well did they get Fuel from the Hopper?
How well did they get Fuel from the floor?
How well did they get Fuel from the feeder?
How well did they get Gears from the floor?
How well did they get Gears from the feeder?
How well did they put the Gear on the hook?
Roughly what percentage of the high shots succeeded?
Roughly what percentage of the low shots succeeded?
Roughly what percentage of the gears succeeded?
Number of points lost to penalties?
Number of points lost to fouls?
Did their alliance gain a Order Point?

Human player Questions.Question: How did they pull up the gears?
Human player Questions.Comment: All HQ questions are answered from the Human Player scouting tablet

Human player Questions.Question: Did they put the gears in the right order?
Did the human player get a foul?
From which team was the airship (1) human player?

Human player Questions.Question: From which team was the airship (2) human player?
Human player Questions.Comments: Include list of all teams at the event.

Human player Questions.Question: From which team was the runner human player?
Human player Questions.Comments: Include list of all teams at the event.

How did the airship (2) human player do?
How did the runner human player do?
